data.description: NEW PRICE FOR QUICK SALE! Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Santa Clara! This nicely updated home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and modern amenities. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac. The heart of the home features a beautiful kitchen, adorned with cherry wood cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, making this kitchen a chef's delight. The stunning bamboo flooring adds an elegant touch throughout the home, with a charming fireplace as the focal point in the family room, creating a cozy atmosphere for those chilly evenings. The bathrooms have been tastefully updated featuring modern fixtures and finishes. Enjoy the convenience of a 2-car garage, providing ample space for parking and storage. The large backyard features a covered patio with plenty of room for the family to run and ample gardening space along with its own well for watering.
